title: Four prominent women in sports and wellness meet at #BigBMeetUp
excerpt: Excellent event on 'Championing Qatari Sportswomen' by #BigBMeetUp and @ISLQatar. @USEmbassyDoha is a strong supporter of women in sports and committed to empowering women and girls.
notes: Exact publication date unknown; event mentioned recently by Ambassador Greta C. Holtz and The Peninsula Qatar tweet dated 1 day ago.
